name: John 4 John Funk
description: It is a "must" to do a window in the Hic Et Nunc space at this point. John has allowed artists to use his window concept to add our own unique touches and incorporate our styles with his. In learning what my style would be, I felt that this was a perfect opportunity to create a window of my own! I am grateful that John has been so welcoming to all of the artists who have used his style as a foundational concept to a semi original art piece.
